version:  1.55.0      date: 12/18/2009 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

12/18
	Rewrote initialization of parallel wavefunction data so parallel
	allocation is delayed until data is actually loaded or initialized
	(from randomize_wf or run -atomic_density).  Before this, the data
	was allocated at the outset and then reallocated every time a
	variable like nrowmax or ecut was set.
	
