version:  1.52.0      date: 9/25/2009 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

09/25
	Added spin polarization, controlled with spin variable (e.g. set
	spin 1.0).  Added SlaterDet.copyTo function to allow reshaping of
	wf data from larger contexts to smaller ones, needed for loading
	nspin=2 XML checkpoint data.

	Added error exit to BOSampleStepper when PSDA is used with nite=1
	and empty states, since PSDAWavefunctionStepper calculates acceleration between 
	current wf (diagonalized) and stored copy (unrotated).
		
