------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	
version:  1.36.0      date:  11/29/2007
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

11/29
	Added qbLink interface, a static library which can provide full
	Qbox functionality to other codes, allowing for mixed-physics
	calculations e.g. thermodynamic integration.  Cout is redirected
	to a separate file (filename set in qbLink constructor) during
	Qbox operations.
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	
version:  1.35.1      date:  10/24/2007
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

10/24
	Implemented Lowe and Andersen thermostats using code from
	Francois.  MDIonicStepper was changed so that thermostats and
	center of mass velocity subtraction occurs within compute_vp, and
	velocity changes are applied to v0 (v(t)) rather than vhalf
	(v(t-0.5dt)) as before.

10/24
	Fixed bug in ThresholdScf in which convergence was incorrectly
	detected with nsteps = 2.  Rewrote SimpleConvergenceDetector to
	only look for convergence when the history list size was >=
	nsteps.

