------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	
version:  1.32.7      date:  5/1/2007
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	

5/1
	Added support for isosurface output of both density and wave
	function to save and saveden commands.  Currently only gOpenMol
	and Molmol formats are supported.  The Gaussian "cube" format
	requires values on a grid with z varying fastest, which requires a
	lot more communication and more complicated implementation, so it
	has not been implemented yet.	

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	
version:  1.32.6      date:  4/30/2007
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	

4/30
	Added conditional test before calling MPI_Comm_free in Context.C
	to check that comm_ != MPI_COMM_NULL.  Subcommunicators must be
	created from all processes in the main communicator, but will be
	set to MPI_COMM_NULL for all processes not in subcommunicator.
	Although it doesn't cause an error on all platforms (e.g. thunder,
	bgl), calling MPI_Comm_free with MPI_COMM_NULL is incorrect, and
	will cause a crash on atlas and purple.
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	
version:  1.32.5      date:  4/20/2007
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	

4/20
	Rewrote SlaterDet constructor so that single-column contexts are passed as an argument.
	This prevents an MPI error on Thunder when many k-points are used:  "No more available
	contexts."  
	
