version:  1.25.0      date:  3/8/2006
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	

3/8    	
	Support for forces, empty states and total energies with k-points
	implemented, and rigorously tested against PWSCF.  Symmetry
	averaging not yet supported. 


